name: Fond Spectators
description:
Digital illustration work hand drawn by artist Mass Graven Image who is based in Austin Texas.
The imaginary world of colors and creatures are in the main field of focus for this image.
I created the basic concept for a good friend many years ago and didn't ever see the place in which it was going to go until I started placing the eyes in as more of an experiment than anything. They all started popping out one by one and I knew that I had been given the final go ahead artistically to turn this piece over on the roster of completed works.
I like that some of the faces are very vague and take a little more time to seek out for the viewer to see.  I hope you enjoy my work. With Love 
~Mass Graven Image.
